Graham Meriwether, director of the 
film "American Meat", discusses the documentary about chicken, 
cattle and hog production in America. Meriwether talks with 
Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Taking Stock."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:57
 